         <abstract encodinganalog="520$a" label="Abstract:">Physician and suffragist.  Papers consists of one box of correspondence, biographical materials, and memorabilia.   The papers of Dr. Mary Olive Hunt relate primarily to her medical career and include cards of matriculation and registration in courses of the New England Female Medical College.  Elizabeth ("Bessie") Bisbee Hunt's correspondence include letters and notes both personal and professional, from famous and lesser known people.
      </abstract>
